  "name": "Divine Smite",
  "type": "feat",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>Starting at 2nd level, when you hit a creature with a melee weapon attack, you can expend one spell slot to deal radiant damage to the target, in addition to the weapon's damage. The extra damage is [[/damage 2d8]] for a 1st-level spell slot, plus [[/damage 1d8]] for each spell level higher than 1st, to a maximum of [[/damage 5d8]]. The damage increases by [[/damage 1d8]] if the target is an undead or a fiend, to a maximum of [[/damage 6d8]].</p></div>",
